  {
    "row": 39,
    "rowsha": "fB5KyDf2iMg/fUM6Ldw3uee32HRYUQ59fiXB8ZP8/lE=",
    "originContent": "## Core Insight",
    "translatedContent": "## 核心见解"
  },
  {
    "row": 40,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 41,
    "rowsha": "IdSRlvN0lsYioBmdzez/2cwCoIW4nMm6YNjeQV87jy8=",
    "originContent": "✨ **Work smarter, not harder.**",
    "translatedContent": "✨ **聪明工作，而不是苦干。**"
  },
  {
    "row": 42,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 43,
    "rowsha": "PzGVDFiA9wtn52t2PSb9J1Ck388CDyhMrr7XIezctng=",
    "originContent": "In the post-training stage of LLMs, instead of blindly adding massive amounts of surface-level diverse text, it is more effective to precisely identify and synthesize those **truly missing key features**. With only a small number of targeted synthetic samples, we can significantly fill the gaps in **Feature Activation Coverage (FAC)**, leading to clear performance improvements on downstream tasks.",
    "translatedContent": "在大语言模型的后训练阶段，与其盲目添加大量表面多样化文本，不如更有效地精准识别和合成那些**真正缺失的关键特征**。仅需少量有针对性的合成样本，我们就能显著填补**特征激活覆盖率（FAC）**的空白，从而在下游任务上带来明显的性能提升。"
  },
  {
    "row": 44,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 45,
    "rowsha": "vjrNG2rZzBOMPAiubx9GUgvbKHR/YAh3jr8nGhCzGLU=",
    "originContent": "### Why is this insight simple yet powerful?",
    "translatedContent": "### 为什么这个洞见简单却强大？"
  },
  {
    "row": 46,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 47,
    "rowsha": "9uS/scTj19vPx40HxIpVqL2l7IsjXYarEHZ3fk0wHhY=",
    "originContent": "Traditional data synthesis focuses on quantity and surface diversity (vocabulary, sentence patterns, topic distribution), but these are often just **weak proxies**. What truly determines a model's downstream performance is **the coverage of key features required by the target task**.",
    "translatedContent": "传统的数据合成关注于数量和表面多样性（词汇、句式、主题分布），但这些通常只是**弱代理**。真正决定模型下游性能的是**目标任务所需关键特征的覆盖率**。"
  },
  {
    "row": 48,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 49,
    "rowsha": "71lpktkW8w9y5JkLdmIeTP36trtYnCHxTQp/t3JTiuc=",
    "originContent": "Our work reveals:",
    "translatedContent": "我们的工作揭示："
  },
  {
    "row": 50,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 51,
    "rowsha": "cWn7N6Ci0X2RV7EG5gVGE10a5G8eULDFswKO/G0mYUA=",
    "originContent": "- Many texts that \"appear very different\" actually activate highly overlapping features;",
    "translatedContent": "- 许多“看起来非常不同”的文本实际上激活了高度重叠的特征；"
  },
  {
    "row": 52,
    "rowsha": "2H3IGsS1sHEH2rwzOd3Pib/jo53GPwi+p7BdkACUvh8=",
    "originContent": "- **FAC** predicts downstream performance much better than standard diversity metrics, including **Distinct-1/2** and **n-gram Entropy** at the word level, **POS-tag Distinct-2** at the syntax level, and **Pair CosDist** and **Semantic Entropy** at the embedding level.  ",
    "translatedContent": "- **FAC**比标准多样性指标更好地预测下游性能，包括词级的**Distinct-1/2**和**n-gram熵**、句法级的**POS-tag Distinct-2**、嵌入级的**Pair CosDist**和**语义熵**。  "
  },
  {
    "row": 53,
    "rowsha": "LYChM4ue/kyubQekm431xPVbSSpd46/JhkaxNv8xf9w=",
    "originContent": "- For instruction following, **FAC Synthesis** achieves performance comparable to the prior SOTA **MAGPIE**, while requiring **150× less data** than MAGPIE.",
    "translatedContent": "- 对于指令遵循，**FAC合成**在仅需**MAGPIE的1/150数据量**的情况下，实现了与先前SOTA **MAGPIE**相当的性能。"
  },
  {
    "row": 54,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
